  "text": "The concept of a characteristic imset was proposed by Studený, Hemmecke and Lindner as an algebraic representative of a BN structure in 2010 [CITATION_1] . Note that the term imset is an acronym for integer-valued multiset and was introduced by Studený [CITATION_2] to name vectors whose components are integers indexed by subsets of a fixed basic set.",
